snippet.title: TY the Tasmanian Tiger 3 Trailer
snippet.description:
CRIKEY! 

TY is back with a brand new adventure, in this fully remastered version of TY the Tasmanian Tiger 3. Pick up your rangs; pull on your shorts, and prepare to rescue the SOUTHERN RIVERS from a brand new threat!!!

http://store.steampowered.com/app/411980/TY_the_Tasmanian_Tiger_3
